# Local development secrets for the Cloudflare Worker (loaded by `vite dev`).
# Copy to `.dev.vars` and fill in. `.dev.vars` is gitignored.
#
# Everything here is OPTIONAL for local dev. The D1 binding (DB) and email
# binding (SEND_EMAIL) come from wrangler.jsonc and run against local emulation;
# Turnstile uses Cloudflare's always-pass test keys when these are unset.

# Cloudflare Turnstile (https://dash.cloudflare.com -> Turnstile).
# Leave unset to use the always-pass test keys in development.
# TURNSTILE_SITE_KEY="0x..."
# TURNSTILE_SECRET_KEY="0x..."
